  <h2>
    <span>喜欢读&#34;北京，北京&#34;的人也喜欢</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3018339/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '3018339', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/view/subject/s/public/s6862126.jpg"/></a>
